ed%20by%20the%20state%20government%20in%202019%20and%20multiple%20times%20at%20the%20district%20level%20in%202017%2C%202021%2C%20and%202023.%20However%2C%20the%20humble%20teacher%20does%20not%20believe%20in%20getting%20recognition%20in%20the%20form%20of%20awards.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20not%20doing%20this%20work%20for%20awards.%20Planting%20trees%20is%20like%20an%20addiction%20to%20me.%20Sometimes%20I%20wonder%20if%20I%20should%20stop%20for%20some%20time%2C%20but%20I%20fail%20to%20do%20so.%20When%20I%20revisit%20the%20plantation%20sites%20and%20watch%20the%20saplings%20grow%20into%20trees%2C%20it%20gives%20me%20immense%20pleasure%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%20All%20photos%3A%20Bheraram%20Bhakhar.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695648211000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D330805%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20government%20school%20teacher%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Bheraram%20Bhakhar%20has%20planted%20more%20than%204.28%20lakh%20trees%20to%20prevent%20desertification%20and%20maintain%20Thar's%20ecological%20balance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330805%2Frajasthan-bheraram-bhakhar-tree-teacher-plants-lakhs-of-native-trees-prevent-desertification%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%229%20GI-Tagged%20Mithais%20You%20Must%20Try%20%26amp%3B%20The%20Amazing%20Stories%20Behind%20Them%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3Emithaiwala%3C%2Fem%3E%20at%20the%20curb%20on%20my%20street%20is%20viewed%20as%20nothing%20less%20than%20God%20by%20his%20patrons%20who%20are%20regulars%20at%20his%20100-square-foot%20shop.%20While%20the%20space%20behind%20the%20glass%20boasts%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F235277%2Findian-traditional-food-d