ion%2C%20ensure%20and%20strengthen%20Rhinoceros%20and%20other%20flagship%20species%E2%80%99%20conservation.%20The%20second%20priority%20would%20be%20the%20utmost%20welfare%20of%20the%20forest%20frontline%20staff%20who%20serve%2024%C3%977%20in%20one%20of%20the%20toughest%20conditions%20at%20Kaziranga%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20it%20has%20only%20been%2020%20days%20since%20Sonali%20assumed%20the%20new%20responsibility%2C%20she%20is%20quite%20geared%20up%20for%20the%20upcoming%20workload.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20great%20responsibility%20and%20I%20am%20thankful%20to%20the%20state%20government%20for%20giving%20me%20the%20opportunity.%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20wait%20to%20give%20my%20best%20to%20nature%20and%20conserve%20the%20wildlife%20of%20the%20national%20park%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20women%20aspiring%20to%20be%20in%20the%20field%20of%20forest%20and%20wildlife%20conservation%20in%20India%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWomen%20and%20young%20ladies%20who%20love%20outdoors%20and%20want%20to%20make%20a%20difference%2C%20be%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20communities%20must%20drop%20all%20their%20apprehensions%20and%20give%20it%20a%20try.%20There%20are%20several%20opportunities%20to%20explore%20and%20the%20sky%E2%80%99s%20the%20limit!%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695303144000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D330465%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sonali%20Ghosh%2C%20who%20assumed%20the%20role%20as%20the%20field%20director%20of%20Kaziranga%20National%20Park%20on%201%20September%2C%202023%2C%20grew%20up%20having%20a%20close%20affinity%20to%20animals.%20By%20the%20time%20she%20completed%20her%20graduation%20in%20life%20sciences%2C%20her%20affinity%20had%20turned%20into%20a%20full%20blown%20passion.%20Being%20in%20forest%20and%2