%20one%20for%20him%2C%20he%20shares.%20He%20has%20had%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20his%20family%20for%20more%20than%20three%20decades.%20He%20credits%20his%20wife%20for%20being%20a%20big%20reason%20for%20his%20success.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20wife%20is%20my%20rock.%20She%20supported%20me%20since%20the%20day%20we%20got%20married.%20She%20also%20helped%20my%20younger%20sister%20get%20married.%20Today%2C%20my%20wife%20is%20a%20successful%20executive%20in%20the%20private%20sector%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Nellayapan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202006%2C%20his%20wife%20and%20children%20moved%20to%20Trivandrum%20because%20of%20his%20wife%E2%80%99s%20job.%20He%20proudly%20mentions%20that%20his%20son%20is%20now%20a%20doctor%2C%20and%20his%20daughter%20is%20in%20Class%2011.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReminiscing%20the%20past%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20concentrate%20only%20on%20work%20because%20I%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20responsibility%20when%20I%20came%20here.%20I%20had%20to%20ensure%20that%20my%20siblings%20studied%20well%20and%20my%20parents%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20borrow%20money.%20Poverty%20and%20responsibility%20guided%20me%20on%20the%20right%20path%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENellayapan%20has%20a%20message%20to%20all%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F306810%2Fthis-heartwarming-story-of-determination-and-resilience-started-with-a-simple-no%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eyoung%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20substitute%20for%20hard%20work.%20You%20might%20get%20the%20reward%20late%2C%20but%20keep%20at%20it.%20Hustle%20for%20a%20better%20tomorrow%20with%20focus.%20You%20will%20be%20rewarded%20for%20your%20efforts.%20Just%20work%20hard%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20let%20your%20mind%20get%20diverted.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20the%20day%2C%20many%20people%20helped%20his%20father%20with%20the%20loans.%20Even%20though%20his%20parents%20don%E2%80%99t%20require%20his%20assistance%20now%2C%20this%20government%20officer%20is%20a%20strong%20believer%20in%20%3Cem%3Ekarma%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Today%2C%20he%20supports%20six%20students%20in%20their%20education.%20%E2%80%9CGod%20has%20blessed%20me%3B%20I%20have%20to%20pass%20on%20the%20help%20to%20those%20who%20need%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oecd-ilibrary.org%2Fsites%2F61d5c87b-en%2Findex.html%3FitemId%3D%2Fcontent%2Fcomponent%2F61d5c87b-en%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EOECD%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695101867000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FNellayapan-1695049811.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D330237%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nellayapan%20B%2C%20Officer%20on%20Special%20Duty%20(OSD)%20to%20the%20Nagaland%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20grew%20up%20in%20crushing%20poverty%20in%20a%20one-room%20house%20in%20a%20village%20in%20Kanniyakumari.%20Exemplifying%20the%20power%20of%20education%2C%20his%20inspiring%20story%20has%20won%20the%20Internet.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330237%2Fnellayapan-b-kanniyakumari-osd-to-nagaland-chief-minister-inspiring-story-went-viral-on-twitter%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22For%2012%20Years%2C%20Chandigarh%20Man%20Has%20Run%20a%20Unique%20%E2%80%98Bird%20Ambulance%20on%20Wheels%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOn%20one%20dark%20night%20in%202011%2C%20a%20sweeper%20was%20cleaning%20the%20streets%20near%20the%20army%20attachment%20camp%20in%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20Ferozepur%20city.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EManjit%20Singh%2C%20a%20former%20drawing%20teacher%2C%20had%20brought%2050%20children%20along%20with%20a%20non-profit%20organisation%20from%20Chandigarh%20to%20the%20camp%20to%20show%20them%20how%20the%20Indian%20Army%20functions.%20On%20stepping%20out%20for%20dinner%2C%20he%20noticed%20something%20strange%20among%20all%20the%20waste%20that%20the%20sweeper%20had%20collected.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoing%20a%20little%20closer%20to%20the%20bin%2C%20he%20realised%20that%20it%20was%20a%20dead%20pigeon!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20asked%20the%20sweeper%20why%20she%20was%20throwing%20the%20body%20in%20a%20dustbin.%20I%20even%20inquired%20how%20it%20died.%20She%20informed%20me%20that%20the%20bird%20got%20electrocuted.%20Similarly%2C%20another%20had%20died%20nearby%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20next%20four%20days%20at%20the%20camp%2C%20the%2054-year-old%20could%20not%20forget%20the%20incident.%20He%20pondered%20on%20finding%20a%20solution%20that%20would%20be%20beneficial%20for%20both%20the%20birds%2C%20and%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmanjit-singh-2-1695045261.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Manjit%20converted%20his%20bicycle%20into%20a%20%E2%80%98bird%20ambulance%E2%80%99.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmanjit-singh-2-1695045261.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmanjit-singh-2-1695045261-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmanjit-singh-2-1695045261-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmanjit-singh-2-16950