care%20doctor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%2042-year-old%20man%20and%20two%20of%20the%20four%20admitted%20tested%20positive%20for%20Nipah%20virus.%20Three%20others%20have%20also%20tested%20positive%20in%20Kozhikode%2C%20taking%20the%20total%20Nipah%20cases%20currently%20to%20six.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20this%2C%20Dr%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20team%20has%20helped%20the%20state%20government%20establish%20containment%20zones%20and%20trace%20all%20contacts%20of%20these%20patients%20and%20isolate%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%202018%20experience%20helped%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FF6ERlubaYAA9NDF-1694787971.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kerala%20government%20has%20increased%20surveillance%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FF6ERlubaYAA9NDF-1694787971.jpg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FF6ERlubaYAA9NDF-1694787971-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FF6ERlubaYAA9NDF-1694787971-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FF6ERlubaYAA9NDF-1694787971-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FF6ERlubaYAA9NDF-1694787971-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330119%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKerala%20government%20has%20increased%20testing%20and%20created%20containment%20zones%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20enabled%20Dr%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20quick%20thinking%20was%20his%20experience%20in%202018.%20He%20was%20part%20of%20the%20team%20at%20Baby%20Memorial%20Hospital%2C%20Kozhikode%2C%20who%20had%20identified%20the%20first%20cases%20of%20the%20virus%20in%20the%20state%20in%20May%202018.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20time%2C%20Dr%20Kumar%20recalls%2C%20three%20members%20of%20a%20family%20were%20admitted%20with%20fever.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20patient%20had%20severe%20encephalitis%20(inflammation%20of%20the%20brain).%20On%20evaluation%2C%20we%20found%20that%20his%20brother%20had%20died%20two%20weeks%20back%20with%20unusual%20symptoms.%20So%20the%20same%20three%20conditions%2C%20clustering%20of%20cases%2C%20unusual%20clinical%20symptoms%2C%20and%20contact%20with%20an%20index%20case%20gave%20us%20suspicion%20of%20a%20rare%20virus.%20Some%20symptoms%20mimicked%20Nipah%20and%20we%20sent%20the%20sample%20to%20Manipal%20virology%20institute%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20patients%20also%20lived%20near%20Janaki%20forest%2C%20home%20to%20many%20bat%20species.%20Fruit%20bats%20in%20a%20forest%20area%20here%20had%20tested%20positive%20for%20Nipah%20in%202018.%20Coincidentally%2C%20Dr%20Kumar%20hails%20from%20Ulliyeri%20village%2C%20which%20is%20just%2020%20kms%20from%20Janaki%20forest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Nipah%20outbreaks%20in%202018%2C%202019%20and%202021%20all%20presented%20with%20encephalitis%20symptoms.%20However%2C%20this%20time%2C%20the%20symptoms%20are%20flu-like%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20for%20diagnosis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20symptoms%20mimic%20flu%2C%20along%20with%20some%20central%20nervous%20system%20symptoms%20like%20confusion%2C%20convulsions%2C%20seizures.%20This%20time%20the%20presentation%20is%20very%20different.%20This%20is%20the%20season%20when%20influenza%20and%20pneumonia%20cases%20are%20a%20lot.%20We%20have%20to%20look%20carefully%20at%20family%20history%20and%20blood%20work.%20Most%20of%20these%20patients%20have%20low%20platelet%20count%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Dr%20Kumar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20doctor%20was%20part%20of%20the%20medical%20teams%20in%202018%20and%202023%20who%20first%20diagnosed%